The paper deals with the problem of active learning, which is a subfield of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). It also involves information acquisition (cs.IT) and decision making (cs.SY). The paper uses a heuristic policy based on maximizing divergence, which is a common technique in data science (cs.DS).
